Six more county assemblies on Tuesday passed the Building Bridges Initiative (BBI) Bill. 

Murang'a Mombasa, Lamu, Nyeri and Makueni county assemblies endorsed the draft unanimously. 

Kakamega ward representatives approved the bill with only two out of the 89 MCAs voting against the draft. 

